{"tid":1489746,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"成立大台!!不分和勇 共同升級 今個星期集火傾點升級 等死線後 勇武和理都可即日升級","createTime":"2019-08-20T02:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T12:22:12.000Z","uid":33668,"like":4,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3bf5e7cb0a7f4d3277e1da8e7fdbd06fa5d59205","tid":1489746,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:53:12.000Z","msg":"成立大台 共繪未來香港藍圖!!<br />\n<br />\n以下含藍絲用語 用嚟將理念推廣出去俾所有香港人<br />\n<br />\n事情已經到咗克不容緩 就算<strong>23號要即刻升級 但無方向無walk through plan無攻略 </strong><br />\n<strong>香港人會hai 升</strong> <ins>又係做返塞鐵果D不合作 ...講真 無咩用</ins><br />\n<br />\n所以我建議配合未來政局/警察改革 成立大台!! <strong>呢個大台就係民間系列喇!</strong><br />\n我建議以設短中長期目標 以大家未來想見嘅方法設立民間政府及執法組織<br />\n<br />\n短期目標 係要市民同民間<strong>先習慣民主 實踐民主 對將來成立民間議會成為台階</strong> 亦令多D人對香港人嘅自制力同思考/學習速度 有信心<br />\n<br />\n另外 成立<strong><ins>民安隊</ins></strong> <strong>保護本土及示威者安全 亦包括民安隊糾察隊</strong> (比照未來監警會/獨立調查委員會架構) <span style=\"color: red;\">以約制武</span><br />\n<br />\n中線 再者 國際線 <strong>配合攬炒 成立海關 (海外關注組)</strong> 負責定立海外抵制嘅港共官員名單定期發送海外各國 配合歐美日制裁行動如凍結戶口 不發出旅遊簽證 不容許在列名單參與國際活動交流 <br />\n(諗下林奠唔可以親身出藉國際活動 要派下面D 二三線官員出藉 佢剩係可以參加大陸會 諗起都開心 另外林奠想去德國睇自己個德國寶畢業?? NO WAY!! 一哥唔可以做聯合國相關會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n以上兩個目標 必需要多方面參與<br />\n1) 文宣<br />\n2) 武勇<br />\n3) 專業人士 對以上組織有知識嘅人<br />\n4) 孫中山系野人 - 負責聯絡各國 增加臨時組織認受性同有民主建構經驗嘅人共繪藍圖<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論:<br />\n<br />\n中長線: 成立民間立法會 普選市民認受嘅議員 包括區議員(並佔據所有地方組織如業立案)同立法會<br />\n<br />\n中長線: 民安結合專業結構 相關牌照 參加國際/聯合國認可嘅國際組織 增加認受性成為有影響力嘅執法單位 增加法院承認民安隊舉證的信心進而打擊警察證供不可信程度<br />\n<br />\n終極目標: 要國際認可大台 成為海外海內所有咨詢香港事務嘅其中一環重要指引 比香港政府同等或更具認受性<br />\n<br />\n正名:<br />\n以上含藍絲用語 用嚟將理念推廣出去俾所有香港人<br />\n<br />\n大台 - 要增加認受性同效率 但<ins>唔附予大台有權去代示威者deal 任何嘢</ins> 一切要經民授形式決定如公投 形式類近民間記者會<br />\n<br />\n民安=糾察隊? - 極具爭議 我都係拋磚引玉 但相對於雨革時期會有割席派別 今次核彈都唔覺 我認為以和勇派為骨幹加上民安隊成員在陣可構成服從同執法公正嘅同時亦無阻武勇行動升級 對裡對外對武勇和理都有公信力 另外糾察隊同武勇並唔需要從屬關係"},{"pid":"95e9165ac1a66d6783f2c0bb23015014568454de","tid":1489746,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:53:38.000Z","msg":"每5小時一推<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"270d9ac0c886fb63b39cf86958bfd1a2cfde64b8","tid":1489746,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:57:57.000Z","msg":"以上係方向 理論<br />\n<br />\n亦希望熟知法律 國際法 中英聯合聲名 基本法等嘅專業人士 可以從根本將空論結構論述 或怎樣組織化包括民安隊及民間立法會"},{"pid":"d696ce1e05dded9cb6f5a50f73c83fde14d6dd8a","tid":1489746,"uid":85082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:00:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦大台"},{"pid":"31f9766d323b2cdd3e4fbf689dbdfcaace48b177","tid":1489746,"uid":85082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:02:25.000Z","msg":"你可以建立組織代表你自己果堆人<br />\n但你唔好諗住起大台控制其他人"},{"pid":"6f9e2a037c79fdedf9ff00dfa78d85680d6e39c9","tid":1489746,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:06:21.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉 希望負評嘅幫手修改<br />\n出文前我唔知23號有HK WAY活動<br />\n不分化不割席 我支持和你拖活動<br />\n<br />\n另外 非死兜 用字上我有意用大家聽唔入耳嘅字眼係想brainstorm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知寫成立大台真係食硬負評 <br />\n<br />\n但我心目中大台係<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不具備同政府談判嘅權力</span></ins></strong> 目的當然唔想整一個可以出賣示威者嘅大台 而係用於推動和勇升級的一個措施<br />\n包括公投<br />\n包括民間/臨時立法會<br />\n亦包括民安隊組成 / 聯絡 / 行動整合"},{"pid":"428d7e6ddf843ec940396783d1541d7c943bca13","tid":1489746,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:11:46.000Z","msg":"大台 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd7225d361ad59c0848fa50e55d481fa2a883b6","tid":1489746,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:13:07.000Z","msg":"歡迎有意討論者討論及俾意見 多謝<br />\n另外 亦歡迎大家反對嘅不推文回覆 正反意見都接受"},{"pid":"8722c622cc877d6d8b4fe4a2ebd22ce3ed5ee61b","tid":1489746,"uid":10070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c39742983a8d786433dca1bb5207430af60cc1d","tid":1489746,"uid":130996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:17:29.000Z","msg":"大你老母閪呀"},{"pid":"b08ee07d4cef4028faf824968d8a82c20b99154a","tid":1489746,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8722c622cc877d6d8b4fe4a2ebd22ce3ed5ee61b","tid":1489746,"uid":10070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家<strong>反對嘅用不推文回覆</strong>呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我幫你不推文回覆<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">多D反大台嘅人 都可以對諗下成立大台嘅人有恫嚇作用</span></strong>都係我希望嘅目標<br />\n<br />\n另外詳見底下正名部份 有我對於大你老母台嘅睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0917c571dab3c53624e0269b1cbc33bd1d11ae18","tid":1489746,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:23:57.000Z","msg":"新方向:<br />\n<br />\n民間旅發局 - 定立定期資訊發佈渠道 以中英日等語言 發佈示威受影響區域及交通安排建議等資訊<br />\n<br />\n同時亦可作為推廣香港特色旅遊建議參與路線 例如上週維園參與路線建議同交通建議 及嚟緊23號和理牽嘅參與路線及市民交通安排<br />\n<br />\n亦可安排車隊<br />\n<br />\n及宣揚國際參與反送中的消息及交通安排<br />\n<br />\n目的都係增加認受性同埋俾多D 機會 掌握從政經驗<br />\n<br />\n(我工作中 會盡量每3小時 用諗法去推呢個POST 希望就算無大台 但以上IDEA 都可以俾各界別同路人參考同啟發 或用唔同形式/非大台形式實行)"},{"pid":"264568e2daf14d2ceca7aed3c7cd5d97bb473e5c","tid":1489746,"uid":199227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:24:38.000Z","msg":"大你老母台"},{"pid":"5fedf53d5cf182301e24db505e18caf725ef5989","tid":1489746,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:27:02.000Z","msg":"本人老粗小市民 字都唔識多個<br />\n但求拋磚引玉<br />\n<br />\n目的係推動還政於民嘅前期工作 同建立土壤去推動呢樣嘢"},{"pid":"57f4d470450a8d5201c9e7f1f614ec096b05082f","tid":1489746,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:30:42.000Z","msg":"大你老母台"},{"pid":"a805b149cc2fe9a61f8d292bc6ee064e422af6bc","tid":1489746,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:54:21.000Z","msg":"屌早知唔寫大台兩隻字漏屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新建議: 成立經貿組織<br />\n制定紅商/支持送中明單 定期UPDATE 等海外公司簽誇國合同時參考<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於罷買或支持購買活動影響小商店對大局影響唔夠<br />\n所以 希望將紅商名單 中英日翻譯 設立網站定期宣傳及更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想海外投起高鐵/基建/網路等大形項目? NO WAY!<br />\n想賺海外錢 外匯? 問過我先!"},{"pid":"1dc133884260630600ce5ad8eb871fcbcd43c4de","tid":1489746,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a805b149cc2fe9a61f8d292bc6ee064e422af6bc","tid":1489746,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:54:21.000Z","msg":"屌早知唔寫大台兩隻字漏屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新建議: 成立經貿組織<br />\n制定紅商/支持送中明單 定期UPDATE 等海外公司簽誇國合同時參考<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於罷買或支持購買活動影響小商店對大局影響唔夠<br />\n所以 希望將紅商名單 中英日翻譯 設立網站定期宣傳及更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想海外投起高鐵/基建/網路等大形項目? NO WAY!<br />\n想賺海外錢 外匯? 問過我先!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:57:19.000Z","msg":"另外 亦可以幫同路人商戶招商 及本身同路人喺公司有決策權嘅 都可以選擇嘅友好商店 *但不建議用名單 怕變相成為對家抵制 及間接令參與商戶受害"},{"pid":"fc8c22b1f2561ebfe078f97b107125d21a8e91f5","tid":1489746,"uid":232671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:59:01.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"16682e95766e69a186456800cf081ce051023bc3","tid":1489746,"uid":118665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T04:59:58.000Z","msg":"大台一定要收皮"},{"pid":"17c5399710e97b2ecf8209dff700049a6b6e1311","tid":1489746,"uid":265032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:57:31.000Z","msg":"先唔講大台嘅問題<br />\n你話成立民安隊，我真係想問樓主係無聽過民安隊定當佢地死左？<a href=\"https://www.cas.gov.hk/chi/about/about_service.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cas.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fabout%2Fabout_service.html&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex3ejezXkYyU2Z26LisGJHUw%3D&h=a75ad45b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cas.gov.hk/chi/about/about_service.html</a>"},{"pid":"9b49f73c6a7895663275dc7119118ac8a278b8fe","tid":1489746,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17c5399710e97b2ecf8209dff700049a6b6e1311","tid":1489746,"uid":265032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:57:31.000Z","msg":"先唔講大台嘅問題<br />\n你話成立民安隊，我真係想問樓主係無聽過民安隊定當佢地死左？<a href=\"https://www.cas.gov.hk/chi/about/about_service.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cas.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fabout%2Fabout_service.html&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex3ejezXkYyU2Z26LisGJHUw%3D&h=a75ad45b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cas.gov.hk/chi/about/about_service.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:01:47.000Z","msg":"諗唔到三個字嘅名嘛<br />\n<br />\n民衛隊 民防隊 自民隊 真警隊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喊咗早知唔玩標題撚 個個以為我起大台起糾察<br />\n<br />\n我都不推文回覆喇"},{"pid":"2bd8c45313b35108bd2237939d88ec52f580a19d","tid":1489746,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每次推POST 我都會加10個負評 一齊拆大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武如何升級 我暫未有談及 或者係未諗到 (諗到都唔應該呢度講)<br />\n<br />\n都係集中咗喺後勤 和理非 可以做嘅事情出發"},{"pid":"5d026cdbb445a1d78ae597c82171d481250ab28e","tid":1489746,"uid":305667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:44:40.000Z","msg":"唔大台啊 唔要啊<br />\n大你老母收得皮未"},{"pid":"fb7ac119751d62194f542626e5d4f375c911a6c8","tid":1489746,"uid":298270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:44:52.000Z","msg":"留比你做最大果個。。。。"},{"pid":"860520b50dcb8c6385e872bcf39abb495139cf17","tid":1489746,"u